<p>Buying or selling property is an important decision, perhaps the most important you&rsquo;ll ever make. Because of the lasting effect such decisions can have on your emotional well-being---and your wallet---it&rsquo;s imperative that you utilize the most talented experts available to gain every advantage.</p>
<p>And here we are.</p>
<h4>Meet Advantage Realty.</h4>
<p>Richard Ellis, Jr., President and Broker of The Advantage Realty Group, Inc., has assembled an amazing team of the most skilled realty specialists in the area. With decades of experience under our roof, we are eminently qualified to lead you through any real estate transaction, advising and educating you through each step of the process. We&rsquo;re experts on the local area. It&rsquo;s our goal to know more about this part of West Alabama than any other agency. Let us guide you through the scenic Tuscaloosa/Northport area, and show you and your family its extraordinary history and its bright future. We know every neighborhood, every school and its administration, and we keep a close watch on the local economy and market conditions. Looking for your University of Alabama gameday headquarters? A cozy hideaway on Lake Tuscaloosa? Perhaps a river retreat on the picturesque Black Warrior? Whether you&rsquo;re buying or selling, we&rsquo;ll work with you until the desired outcome is reached. Consider us your devoted ally and determined negotiator. Your success is our success.</p>
<p>Welcome to Advantage Realty. We&rsquo;ve been waiting for you!</p>
